"{\"uid\": \"etonline.com-hoda-kotb-emotionally-reunites-with-her-daughters-after-covering-paris-olympics-230200\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Hoda Kotbhad a joyous reunion this week after returning from covering the2024 Olympic Gamesin Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\", \"score\": 0.5882352802235369, \"rank\": 0.6999999999999931, \"text\": \"Hoda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999858309822, \"rank\": 1.4169002744659943e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday, Kotb shared a touching video of the moment she was reunited with her daughters, Haley, 7, and Hope, 4.\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_The_Order_of_the_Stick\", \"score\": 0.9951096916872968, \"rank\": 0.004878833891367873, \"text\": \"Haley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_The_Order_of_the_Stick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_The_Order_of_the_Stick\"}, {\"begin\": 208, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope_Williams_Brady\", \"score\": 0.999973491978432, \"rank\": 2.6508724230237055e-05, \"text\": \"Hope\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope_Williams_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hope_Williams_Brady\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Kotb walked through the door, her daughters' excitement was palpable.\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Mommy!\\\"\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"they shouted, running eagerly to greet her.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Haley, dressed in a pink dress, was the first to reach her mom, enveloping her in a warm hug before she could even make it inside.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 344, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_The_Order_of_the_Stick\", \"score\": 0.9951096916872968, \"rank\": 0.004878833891367873, \"text\": \"Haley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_The_Order_of_the_Stick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_The_Order_of_the_Stick\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb, carrying a bouquet of yellow roses and her bag, was overjoyed to be back home.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hope, sporting a Spider-Man dress, could not wait for her hug before showing her mom a water bottle in hand, exclaiming, \\\"Mom, look!\\\"\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The heartwarming moment captured the pure joy of the reunion as the three settled on the couch for some much-needed cuddles.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the Olympics, Kotb stayed connected with her daughters, sharing photos of them cheering on Team USA from home.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9950778015871079, \"rank\": 0.004932895163542864, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regular FaceTime calls kept them close despite the distance.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, Kotb even posted a screenshot from a special call that included her mother, her daughters, and superstar gymnast Simone Biles.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb'sTodayshow team also surprised her during the Aug. 2 broadcast with a video from her daughters.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressed in Team USA gear-Haley Joy in a leotard similar to those worn by the gold-winning women's gymnastics team-the girls sent their mom loving messages.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9950778015871079, \"rank\": 0.004932895163542864, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hi Mommy, we love you and miss you,\\\" they said.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Go Team USA.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go U.S.A.!\\\"\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Kotb, along with co-anchorSavannah Guthrieand weatherman Al Roker, has returned to New York City, theTodayshow continues to maintain a strong presence in Paris.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Roker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Al Roker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Roker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Roker\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 