], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Feldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Feldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But honestly, we are working.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When they get a little bit older and... have a little more independence, we would love to bring our kids to the Olympics... We miss them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb agreed, but noted that she's learned a valuable lesson in her time away.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's also teaching us that kids are fine when we are away for a few days.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are perfectly fine,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been FaceTiming our kids and communicating with them.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes we feel like we have to be there all the time and [then] we realize they are growing, they are thriving, they are excited.\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not wait to get home and see them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED CONTENT:  Video  News  News  News  Streaming  News\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": []}]}"